VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT ConvertTo-SecureString\s+.*-AsPlainText\s+-Force
WHEN EXPR MISSING:Get-Secret|[System\.Environment]::GetEnvironmentVariable|$env:|placeholder|example|test
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects ConvertTo-SecureString usage with -AsPlainText -Force flags indicating a plaintext credential workflow.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for ConvertTo-SecureString with PlainText.
